90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-ho%C3%A1n-ty/poem-CCjI-EDLVLwxhRVUPM9kRw">Tây Hồ hoán ty - 西湖浣絲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-GrfZ83486gEgzshT4ctASA">Đoàn Nguyễn Tuấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%C3%A3n-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-ni%C3%AAn-V%C3%A2n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0/poem-6YXs2qoM-0pPFaxDDrLTew">Vãn đồng niên Vân Đình tiến sĩ Dương thượng thư - 輓同年雲亭進士楊尚書</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/Xu%C3%A2n-giang/poem-luXdlRE6kX2YV2IiBG8yQg">Xuân giang - 春江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/author-mhAlF-W1JHQDMsH_S0aV3Q">Hà Như</a>)<br></div>	</div>
